author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I've reviewed Architects before and I was impressed. So today I'm reacting to "Blackhole" - the latest single from their forthcoming album "The Sky, The Earth & All Between." The video is cinematic and my own narrative is .....wide-ranging. 

Watch Architects "Blackhole" in full: https://youtu.be/8SoLPeFquLM?si=uJ-bs-XnIvg-aEmF

The new Darkness album which comes out in March, you can pre-order 'Dreams On Toast' on CD, vinyl or cassette here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/
Stream / Download the latest single 'I Hate Myself': https://thedarkness.lnk.to/ihm

The Darkness are also going on tour across the UK in March, tickets are on sale here: https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

For Cameo messages from Justin: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

Talk to me on my Patreon:  http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

#reaction #musicreview #architects
title: Architects: "Blackhole" Reaction & Meanderings
